::Striker::

Striker's eyes widen as Spears kisses him, his arms sliding down to her waist 
and around her, pressing her to him. It felt strange laying there in the dump 
that once was the Ark, covered with soot, kissing a femm, but it felt 
allright.

He leans slightly back, looking down at her and smiling before he leans in to 
kiss her again.
